tug79835@temple.edu, tuk48200@gmail.com, and tuj91536@temple.edu. Joey, Ryan, and Sam.

## What will (likely) be the title of your project?

The Maze

## In just a sentence or two, summarize your project. (E.g., "A website that lets you buy and sell stocks.")

Our program will allow the user to input responses that will direct them through a maze. There will only be one correct sequence of answers that will allow the user to reach the end of the maze.

## In a paragraph or more, detail your project. What will your software do? What features will it have? How will it be executed?

As noted, there will only be one sequence of answers that will allow the user to reach the end of the maze. We will be using Unity as the software to power the program. The program will ask the user for inputs within the maze. The correct sequence will allow the user to navigate the maze to the final destination. A wrong choice will send the player back so they can try again. 

